reactDocgen.description:
Rucio Logo SVG Component

A theme-aware logo component that uses currentColor to inherit text color.
The logo automatically adapts its fill color based on the parent's text color,
making it easy to support light and dark themes.

@example
```tsx
// Light theme: dark logo
<RucioLogo className="text-neutral-900" width={146} height={146} />

// Dark theme: light logo
<RucioLogo className="text-neutral-100" width={146} height={146} />

// Theme-aware with Tailwind dark mode
<RucioLogo className="text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100" width={146} height={146} />
```

